OL,3,CCustomers left to camp overnight in
OL,4,CGuernsey Airport after storm
OL,6,FSome Blue Islands' passengers were
OL,7,Fleft to sleep on the terminal floor at
OL,8,FGuernsey Airport on Saturday night (7
OL,9,FSeptember) after their flight was
OL,10,Fcancelled due to bad weather.
OL,12,FThe 8:25pm SI4432 service was called
OL,13,Foff at 9:30pm following heavy
OL,14,Frainfall, thunder and lightning.
OL,16,FA total of 19 passengers were affected
OL,17,Fand nine ended up sleeping at the
OL,18,Fairport as they could not find
OL,19,Fanywhere to stay at short notice.
