OL,3,CCustomers left to camp overnight in
OL,4,CGuernsey Airport after storm
OL,6,FTina Caldeira from Jersey and Nikolas
OL,7,FAppleman from The Netherlands were
OL,8,Famong those who found themselves
OL,9,Fwithout accommodation for the night.
OL,11,FThey say if it was not for the kind
OL,12,Fnature of airport staff and volunteers
OL,13,Ffrom the emergency action Civil
OL,14,FProtection group, they would not have
OL,15,Feven been given a sleeping bag or
OL,16,Fwater.
OL,18,FTina explains: "It's appalling and I
OL,19,Fthink we all felt it was appalling,
OL,20,Fthere was no contact from them (Blue
OL,21,FIslands).
