OL,3,CCustomers left to camp overnight in
OL,4,CGuernsey Airport after storm
OL,6,F"I don't know if they even really knew
OL,7,Fthey had passengers left behind who
OL,8,Fhad nowhere to go and that's just not
OL,9,Facceptable. We could have been unable
OL,10,Fto help ourselves in any way. Each of
OL,11,Fus spent a lot of money buying those
OL,12,Fflights and we really deserve to be
OL,13,Flooked after."
OL,15,FNikolas adds: "I didn't get any
OL,16,Fmessage from Blue Islands, no email,
OL,17,Fso I was informed by my fellow
OL,18,Fpassengers."
