OL,3,CCustomers left to camp overnight in
OL,4,CGuernsey Airport after storm
OL,6,FThe airport cafe opened earlier than
OL,7,Fusual on Sunday morning so that
OL,8,Fpassengers could have hot drinks and
OL,9,Ffood.
OL,11,FSome of those affected told ITV News
OL,12,Fthat they returned by ferry at their
OL,13,Fown expense on Sunday as the next
OL,14,Favailable flight was not until Monday,
OL,15,Fclaiming Blue Islands still had not
OL,16,Fcontacted them about the disruption.
