OL,4,CGuernsey Airport after storm
OL,6,FIn a statement, the airline explain:
OL,7,F"Hotels in Guernsey were full, our
OL,8,Fairport representatives explored other
OL,9,Foptions with local authorities,
OL,10,Fhowever no alternative accommodation
OL,11,Foptions were available.
OL,13,F"We thank Guernsey Airport for keeping
OL,14,Fthe terminal open and providing
OL,15,Fprovisions for passengers.
